title: DeathRepeat_Monster_1
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Back so soon? C’mon. Up! You haven’t gotten to the good part yet!
===


title: DeathRepeat_Monster_2
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Aw, I was sure you had it that time. Maybe next round.
===


title: DeathRepeat_Monster_3
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Ahaha! The hotshot Hunter gets killed by a runty monster?
The Judge: I expect better from an enforcer of Justice. Back you go~
===


title: DeathRepeat_Monster_4
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Cyrus, I don’t know what memories you traded away while you were down there, but remember-
The Judge: You’re supposed to [i]kill[/i] the monsters, not give them hugs. Okay?
===


title: DeathRepeat_Monster_5
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Ouch. I’m glad that wasn’t me. Let’s hope you get luckier on your next run~
===


title: DeathRepeat_Monster_6
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: You have a very [i]unique[/i] fighting style.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Is that an insult or a compliment?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: No, no, just an observation. Now get back in there and keep doing... whatever you’re doing.
===


title: DeathRepeat_Monster_7
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Hello?
The Judge: Hhhheeelllooo!

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: ...

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Oh! You’re finally awake.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: ???

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Alright, let’s do this slowly.
The Judge: Name. Do you remember that muc-

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: ??????

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Pff, just messing with you~ The look on your face was priceless!
===


title: DeathRepeat_Monster_8
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Cyrus, Cyrus... Keep stalling like this, and Prism’s going to wind up the last world saved from the Assimilation.
The Judge: Our current success rate is about... let’s see... six or seven percent.
The Judge: But that number’s going up every cycle, and [i]you’re[/i] getting left behind~
===


title: DeathRepeat_FalseHuman_P1_1
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: I’m still getting used to this whole dying over and over thing.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: If I can handle eons babysitting you enforcers, [i]you[/i] can handle a few more centuries of this.
===


title: DeathRepeat_FalseHuman_P1_2
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: I have to stop that monster. Send me back, now.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Well, someone’s feeling heroic.
===


title: DeathRepeat_FalseHuman_P1_3
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Is that thing even killable?!

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: I wouldn’t be sending you down there otherwise, now would I?
The Judge: Well, I actually have no idea, but it’s worth a shot!
===


title: DeathRepeat_FalseHuman_P2_1
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Having fun?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: I wouldn’t call it [i]fun[/i].
===


title: DeathRepeat_FalseHuman_P2_2
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Tch. Need to dodge that attack next time...

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Yeah, yeah, whatever. Back to work!
===


title: DeathRepeat_FalseHuman_P2_3
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Can’t you try something different next cycle? I’m getting bored of watching this bossfight.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: If Prismatic Security won’t listen to my report, I need to take matters into my own hands.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Eugh. That’s so... [i]Cyrus[/i] of you.
===


title: DeathRepeat_Luna_P4_P5_1
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: That Luna girl is pretty strong, huh? A shame she’s not an enforcer of Justice, I bet [i]she[/i] could have fixed Prism’s timeline by now.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Wow, very encouraging.
===


title: DeathRepeat_Luna_P4_P5_2
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: C’mon, Cyrus~ I didn’t lend you all that Justice power for you to waste it sparring with the cops.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: You think I [i]want[/i] to- nevermind.
===


title: DeathRepeat_Luna_P4_P5_3
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Okay, I know I said it was fun watching you die to a human instead of a monster, but this is getting ridiculous.
The Judge: Jokes are only funny the first time around, you know~
===


title: DeathRepeat_PossessedEve_P4_P5_1
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Hehe, told you Eve was trouble.
===


title: DeathRepeat_PossessedEve_P4_P5_2
---
